data.description: This charming home boasts original hardwood floors , Oak trim , Full enclosed porch and a Brand new roof in 2022 . As well on the back half of the home we have a new addition that creates a 2nd living space with a full bathroom attached to it, equipped with a full roll in shower with skylights on the main floor. Accessible ramp on the side entrance of the home along side of a 1.5 car detached full pull through garage with additional parking next to it. Book your showings , You wont want to miss this one.
